### JavaScript ([script.js](file:///C:/Users/Tomi/Oktat%C3%A1s/fire-escape-room/script.js))
- Update [startGame()](file:///C:/Users/Tomi/Oktat%C3%A1s/fire-escape-room/script.js#41-44): Navigate to `main-menu` instead of `station-1`.
- Create `updateMainMenu()`:
    - Check `gameState.unlockedDigits`.
    - Unlock Station 1 (Always).
