- Update `checkStationX()` functions:
    - On success: [unlockDigit(...)](file:///C:/Users/Tomi/Oktat%C3%A1s/fire-escape-room/script.js#112-125) -> [showFeedback(...)](file:///C:/Users/Tomi/Oktat%C3%A1s/fire-escape-room/script.js#130-142) -> `setTimeout(() => showScreen('main-menu'), 2000)`.
- Add event listeners for the new menu cards.

